image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, OGE Form 278e, for Donald J. Trump. This page, 47 of 51, details 'Part 6: Other Assets and Income', listing various stock funds, bonds, and trusts, along with their values and any income generated.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header containing the form title, instructions, filer's name, and page number. The main body is a table with six columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. The table lists financial assets. A footer at the bottom contains a footnote and a document identifier.
